comment: Plumlee (POR) makes contact with Green's (GSW) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Barnes (GSW) and Aminu (POR) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Curry (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Plumlee's (POR) drive and shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes contact with the ball before making incidental contact with Crabbe (POR).
Thompson (GSW) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Ezeli (GSW) sets the screen on Aminu (POR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact with McCollum's (POR) head on the shot attempt.
Barnes (GSW) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Plumlee (POR) drive to the basket and shot attempt.

[Observable in enhanced video] Plumlee (POR) establishes himself in Curry's (GSW) path, giving him room to avoid the screen. However, he continues to move his hip/leg and contact occurs to his leg area.
Curry (GSW) makes contact with Crabbe (POR) that affects his RSBQ.
Plumlee (POR) does not give Thompson (GSW) room to avoid the screen.
Iguodala (GSW) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Thompson (GSW) makes body contact with Lillard (POR), affecting his shot attempt.
Aminu (POR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Thompson (GSW) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Lillard (POR) makes contact with Curry (GSW) that affects his RSBQ.
